          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-copy-1594054137067-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, finely slice your<strong> cucumber</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>cucumber</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>rice vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and set aside for later – this is your <strong>quick-pickled cucumber</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-1594054150016-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-1594054150016-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-1594054150016-x700.jpg",
