          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-1594054150016-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>shredded kale</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper, then add the <strong>shredded kale</strong> to a large baking tray (or two!) with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Massage the <strong>kale</strong> with clean hands so that the kale is evenly covered in oil</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 5-10 min or until crispy, giving it a good mix up half way through – this is your <strong>crispy kale</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1594054164565-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1594054164565-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
