        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> sesame tofu</strong> with the<strong> edamame brown rice</strong>, <strong>quick-pickled cucumber</strong>, <strong>crispy kale</strong> and a <strong>lime wedge</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the<strong> spicy peanut sauce</strong> over the rice and sesame tofu</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
